      "name": "Halfling Lucky Draw",
      "sources": [
        {
          "link": {
            "alt": "Battlecry! pg. 182",
            "aonid": 268,
            "game-obj": "Sources",
            "name": "Battlecry! pg. 182",
            "type": "link"
          },
          "name": "Battlecry!",
          "page": 182,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "Some halflings, especially those from Varisia, study the methods of Harrow fortune-telling and tap into occult forces that let them manipulate fate using the cards. Some mercenary companies and criminal organizations employ such halflings as bad-luck charms for their enemies.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
