            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The halflings mock and taunt their enemies with quick Harrow readings that predict doom. The troop chooses a number of creatures equal to the number of its remaining segments within 60 feet. Each target must attempt a DC 23 Will save. On a failure, the target must roll their next attack roll, saving throw, or skill check twice and use the worse result.",
